profile:
OGC - Ottawa General Contractors are leaders as Ottawa's design and build renovation experts. Specializing in home renovations, new and custom home construction as well as home design. With our project management and coordination, we're able to efficiently juggle more jobs, large and small, without dropping the ball. 

Ottawa General Contractors are an accredited business with the Ottawa BBB and our CEO, Moe Abbas is a former member of the board of directors for the Better Business Bureau (BBB).. Our skills and expert service has allowed us to expand to other cities in Canada including Vancouver and Calgary in less than 8 years making us one of the fastest growing construction companies. 

We offer warranty following the Tarion warranty guidelines for all our renovations and construction projects. We also have a design center and in house designers available to help you design and build your home. With over 50 years of experience, our team has the knowledge, the tools, the skill-set and the resources to give you the best value for your dollar at unbeatable service. 

We at Ottawa General Contractors understand that you are looking for value with your renovation services. Trust our team to do it right the first time! Call us directly at (613) 225-9991!

Visit our website for all our credentials and more information.

profile:
Why we love what we do

The artist has an East European background and have years of experience as an artist, designer and decorator in Canada.
He has used many art forms and media to express his excellent eye for class, simplicity, style and color that is reflected in his life time of work.
The artistic background combined with his practical skills positioned the artist in the best situation to create designs with most artistically geometric efficient use of canvas space.
These creations have an ergonomic designs with vibrant colors and geometrical style, The elegant and accomplished style incorporates the idea that they can actually be applied to many practically items such t-shirts, towels, stained glass etc.
His unique ability to portray various faces and expressions on a simple geometrical, simplistic design and colors defines his unique and particular Canadian artistry.
One of the most unique traits of this artist is the capacity to create the most representation of personality and emotions with simple strokes and colors.

profile:
www.miniseeds.com

Mini Seeds is the online decorating and room styling resource for families with kids interiors.

Serving the Ottawa Ontario Area and offering online services to other parts of the world.
My mission is to help YOU empower the kids in your life. 

We are a growing interior decorating studio based in Ottawa Ontario, we design and create with kids in mind. We serve families with kids in Ottawa and the surrounding area as well as work with clients online in other parts of the world ? 

When you create a space for kids, a space that talks to them, nourishes and excites them,​ when the rooms they call theirs are decorated according to their personalities and their characters, they will feel important, and that they matter.

When colours are in harmony, shapes and textures are interesting, they will be more curious and opened to learning new discoveries. 

Give them the gift of love, the gift of care and create a place they could always call home​.
